stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> CREATED: 下单
    CREATED --> PAID: 支付成功
    PAID --> ACCEPTED: 商家接单
    ACCEPTED --> SHIPPED: 发货
    PAID --> SHIPPED: 发货(无接单)
    SHIPPED --> RECEIVED: 签收
    RECEIVED --> COMPLETED: 自动/手动确认
    PAID --> AFTERSALE: 申请售后(挂起)
    AFTERSALE --> COMPLETED: 售后完结
    CREATED --> CLOSED: 超时未付
    PAID --> CLOSED: 取消/全额退款
    SHIPPED --> CLOSED: 退货退款完结
    COMPLETED --> [*]
    CLOSED --> [*]
